WEBVTT

01:59.479 --> 02:00.540
What are you doing?

02:00.760 --> 02:01.720
Is this fun?

02:03.400 --> 02:04.800
I don't know what you are talking about.

02:04.800 --> 02:06.200
Move. Don't block my way.

02:06.320 --> 02:07.850
I'm asking you. Is this fun?

02:10.160 --> 02:11.920
Don't you know if it's fun?

02:11.960 --> 02:13.120
I didn't slander you.

02:13.120 --> 02:14.400
Was I wrong?

02:21.079 --> 02:21.960
Xiong Yuanbao.

02:22.440 --> 02:24.520
Are you afraid of others exposing your faults

02:24.520 --> 02:26.079
and calling you an orphan?

02:35.640 --> 02:36.700
What are you doing?

02:39.440 --> 02:40.440
What's going on?

02:40.680 --> 02:42.210
It seems Qiao Yan brought up

02:43.280 --> 02:44.880
Yuanbao's parents first.

02:55.480 --> 02:56.560
Mu Qingyun.

02:59.640 --> 03:02.300
What are you doing? Tearing down the classroom?

03:07.640 --> 03:08.800
You just wait.

03:09.480 --> 03:12.120
Mu Qingyun. Mu Qingyun. Mu Qingyun.

03:17.960 --> 03:18.600
Yuanbao.

03:18.680 --> 03:19.610
Don't come over.

03:20.840 --> 03:21.440
Yuanbao,

03:22.280 --> 03:23.200
listen to me.

03:23.560 --> 03:24.720
I really didn't mean to

03:24.720 --> 03:26.720
tell Mr. Men about your background.

03:26.880 --> 03:28.800
Please don't do anything foolish.

03:28.800 --> 03:29.440
I just...

03:29.520 --> 03:30.280
Mutou,

03:31.960 --> 03:33.560
they are right.

03:33.760 --> 03:36.400
Since I was little, everyone has said the same.

03:36.520 --> 03:37.680
I am an orphan,

03:39.120 --> 03:40.920
a wild child with no parents.

03:42.400 --> 03:44.360
Yes, I am scared.

03:45.040 --> 03:46.079
But being scared

03:46.520 --> 03:48.520
doesn't mean I need others' pity.

03:48.600 --> 03:49.680
Xiong Yuanbao,

03:49.800 --> 03:50.560
how can you say you are

03:50.560 --> 03:51.890
an unwanted wild child?

03:52.079 --> 03:53.000
You have your grandmother

03:53.000 --> 03:53.800
and me.

03:53.920 --> 03:55.520
My parents are your parents.

03:56.200 --> 03:57.730
Whether you admit it or not,

03:57.920 --> 03:59.040
it is the truth.

04:00.160 --> 04:00.880
I know this

04:01.000 --> 04:02.360
has always been a wound in your heart,

04:02.360 --> 04:03.890
untouchable and unspoken.

04:03.960 --> 04:05.360
But you can't live your whole life

04:05.360 --> 04:05.960
like an ostrich,

04:05.960 --> 04:06.960
burying your head in the sand

04:06.960 --> 04:08.620
and refusing to look forward.

04:09.520 --> 04:10.960
If your grandmother knew you were like this,

04:10.960 --> 04:12.240
how sad would she be?

04:12.760 --> 04:13.620
Think about it,

04:13.720 --> 04:16.279
she can look forward with optimism and grace.

04:16.800 --> 04:18.560
Why can't you live in the sun?

04:34.120 --> 04:34.840
Yuanbao.

04:46.400 --> 04:47.460
What are you doing?

04:49.159 --> 04:50.690
Yuanbao, promise me first.

04:50.800 --> 04:52.480
No matter what difficulties you face in the future,

04:52.480 --> 04:54.159
don't ever think about taking your own life.

04:54.159 --> 04:55.440
If something happens to you,

04:55.440 --> 04:57.440
how can I explain it to Grandma?

04:58.159 --> 04:59.960
Who wants to take their own life?

05:00.880 --> 05:03.560
Didn't you tell me to live towards the sun?

05:04.040 --> 05:05.800
I'm just feeling the breeze and the sunshine.

05:05.800 --> 05:06.680
Okay?

05:13.320 --> 05:14.200
Seriously.

05:15.400 --> 05:17.000
You really didn't think that?

05:17.000 --> 05:17.880
No.

05:22.320 --> 05:23.680
Then let's hurry back.

05:25.040 --> 05:26.040
Come on, I'll carry you.

05:26.040 --> 05:26.720
Why?

05:27.120 --> 05:28.850
This way we look more imposing.

05:37.600 --> 05:39.000
What happened to you two?

05:40.120 --> 05:41.600
Yuanbao, are you okay?

05:42.560 --> 05:43.360
I'm fine.

05:43.920 --> 05:45.120
Go back to your seats.

05:46.920 --> 05:47.680
Class.

05:48.600 --> 05:50.640
Taking the opportunity of this class meeting,

05:50.640 --> 05:52.840
I'd like to apologize to Xiong Yuanbao.

05:57.640 --> 05:58.400
Yuanbao.

05:59.080 --> 06:01.240
I was too impulsive today.

06:01.600 --> 06:04.080
I blamed you without finding out the truth.

06:04.320 --> 06:07.280
I didn't think it through,

06:07.400 --> 06:08.800
and acted unfairly.

06:09.360 --> 06:10.890
But teachers are human too,

06:11.200 --> 06:12.400
and we make mistakes.

06:12.880 --> 06:14.120
So right here,

06:14.200 --> 06:16.360
I sincerely apologize to you.

06:19.400 --> 06:20.680
It's fine, teacher.

06:21.400 --> 06:22.200
Qiao Yan.

06:28.600 --> 06:30.040
I talked too much.

06:31.640 --> 06:33.800
I shouldn't have talked behind your back

06:33.800 --> 06:36.120
and said so many mean things.

06:36.360 --> 06:39.680
I hope you won't take it to heart.

06:44.800 --> 06:45.840
I'm sorry.

06:46.400 --> 06:48.000
Being in the same class

06:48.240 --> 06:49.640
is a great destiny.

06:50.000 --> 06:50.920
I hope

06:51.320 --> 06:52.980
you can cherish this destiny.

06:53.360 --> 06:55.360
Shake hands and make up.

06:55.440 --> 06:57.360
Then we need a friendly hug.

06:58.280 --> 07:00.040
Right, let's hug.

07:00.240 --> 07:01.040
Yes.

07:01.120 --> 07:02.800
Yes, exactly.

07:14.440 --> 07:18.040
It doesn't feel good to be talked about behind your back, does it?

07:31.920 --> 07:33.560
Let's go. School is over.

07:38.800 --> 07:39.659
Stop fighting.

07:44.600 --> 07:45.200
Yuanbao.

07:45.840 --> 07:47.320
I know you're suffering.

07:47.640 --> 07:49.040
I'll always be with you.

07:52.960 --> 07:54.020
My sweet daughter.

07:57.560 --> 07:58.720
My sweet daughter, over here.

07:58.720 --> 07:59.520
Yuanbao.

08:03.320 --> 08:03.720
Come here.

08:03.720 --> 08:04.600
Yuanbao.

08:08.080 --> 08:09.010
You called them?

08:09.480 --> 08:11.480
Why are you just standing there? Go.

08:26.640 --> 08:29.240
Yuanbao, we're here to pick you up from school.

08:39.720 --> 08:40.760
107.

08:41.080 --> 08:42.200
108.

08:43.440 --> 08:44.600
109.

08:46.920 --> 08:49.320
The competition is on Yuanbao's birthday.

08:49.920 --> 08:51.720
Such a special day.

08:52.520 --> 08:54.920
What can 109 do?

08:56.480 --> 08:58.120
My mom is so stingy.

08:59.360 --> 09:01.160
Mom and Dad.

09:01.760 --> 09:03.360
I'm going to Shanghai again.

09:03.800 --> 09:05.840
And it happens to be on my birthday.

09:07.280 --> 09:09.600
Did you arrange all of this?

09:11.840 --> 09:13.170
May the trip to Shanghai

09:13.400 --> 09:14.520
be smooth

09:14.920 --> 09:15.960
and safe.

09:16.800 --> 09:17.930
I must win the award.

09:19.360 --> 09:20.220
Xiong Yuanbao,

09:20.880 --> 09:21.720
you can do it!

09:24.120 --> 09:25.450
Second interview site.

09:25.960 --> 09:26.280
New thinking, new expression, real experience.

09:26.280 --> 09:29.010
New thinking, new expression, real experience.

10:28.240 --> 10:29.960
Thank you for just now.

10:30.360 --> 10:32.320
Anyone else would have done the same.

10:32.320 --> 10:34.200
I'm waiting for a car here, so I don't need the umbrella.

10:34.200 --> 10:36.060
The rain might get heavier later.

10:36.280 --> 10:37.720
Take it and go home quickly.

10:37.720 --> 10:38.720
Thank you.

10:39.440 --> 10:40.840
But I'm not a local.

10:40.960 --> 10:43.890
I just came to Shanghai yesterday for a competition.

10:44.400 --> 10:46.680
How about you leave me your contact info?

10:46.800 --> 10:48.280
I'll return the umbrella to you then.

10:48.280 --> 10:49.040
No need.

10:52.640 --> 10:53.560
Wait a moment.

10:55.920 --> 10:56.680
Brother.

10:57.160 --> 10:58.480
Why did it take you so long to answer?

10:58.480 --> 11:00.540
I thought something happened to you.

11:01.080 --> 11:01.960
Me?

11:02.400 --> 11:03.760
I'm at a bus stop near the exam center,

11:03.760 --> 11:05.420
taking shelter from the rain.

11:06.280 --> 11:07.320
Then I'll wait for you.

11:07.320 --> 11:08.720
Call me when you get here.

11:16.000 --> 11:18.860
You don't need to return the umbrella. I'm leaving.

11:19.160 --> 11:20.960
How can I just take your umbrella for nothing?

11:20.960 --> 11:21.600
No.

11:21.680 --> 11:23.360
Give me your contact info,

11:23.480 --> 11:24.760
or your address.

11:24.840 --> 11:26.240
I'll mail it back to you.

11:29.760 --> 11:30.880
I'll be going now.

11:32.200 --> 11:33.760
Thank you!

11:34.800 --> 11:35.800
Wait.

11:36.800 --> 11:37.480
What is it?

11:37.600 --> 11:38.960
Watch out for cars.

11:53.600 --> 11:54.480
Yuanbao.

11:56.280 --> 11:58.520
Why are you so late? I've been waiting for a long time.

11:58.520 --> 11:59.600
Sorry, sorry.

12:00.480 --> 12:02.240
Exam is over. How was it?

12:03.280 --> 12:04.740
I almost didn't make it in.

12:05.400 --> 12:07.530
As long as you took the exam, it's fine.

12:07.960 --> 12:09.080
What was the topic?

12:11.120 --> 12:13.080
I wrote about my parents.

12:19.560 --> 12:21.690
Let's go. I'll take you to a good place.

12:26.680 --> 12:27.800
Since we're here,

12:28.000 --> 12:29.400
whatever you want to play or eat,

12:29.400 --> 12:30.440
just tell me.

12:31.240 --> 12:33.320
Like roller coasters

12:33.440 --> 12:34.520
or something.

12:35.560 --> 12:36.720
Keep bragging.

12:36.880 --> 12:38.540
Aren't you afraid of heights?

12:41.080 --> 12:42.410
That was when I was a kid.

12:42.440 --> 12:44.360
I am not afraid of anything now.

12:45.640 --> 12:47.760
Just watch my performance later.

12:48.160 --> 12:49.720
Hold on to me if you're scared,

12:49.720 --> 12:50.480
got it?

13:21.080 --> 13:22.280
Don't say I know you.

13:37.040 --> 13:37.720
Yuanbao,

13:38.400 --> 13:41.240
I thought you would be touched by the scene

13:41.560 --> 13:43.120
and think of your parents.

13:44.520 --> 13:45.980
That was the last birthday

13:46.760 --> 13:49.080
they spent with me in this life.

13:52.200 --> 13:54.880
I was quite anxious before coming here.

13:56.200 --> 13:57.840
I thought I would be afraid

13:58.320 --> 13:59.440
and resistant.

14:00.520 --> 14:01.880
But after coming here,

14:02.560 --> 14:04.020
I feel much more relieved.

14:05.880 --> 14:06.920
Thank you, Mutou.

14:08.000 --> 14:09.800
No need to be polite with me.

14:10.560 --> 14:11.840
Didn't you say

14:12.000 --> 14:13.600
that we are like

14:13.960 --> 14:15.520
biological sisters?

14:15.800 --> 14:17.200
Shouldn't sisters

14:17.320 --> 14:19.200
share through thick and thin?

14:20.520 --> 14:22.560
Before, when I said we were sisters,

14:22.680 --> 14:24.600
you always said we were brothers.

14:24.800 --> 14:27.800
Why admit you're a beauty today?

14:31.200 --> 14:33.240
Come on.

14:33.440 --> 14:35.320
Since it's your birthday,

14:35.800 --> 14:40.000
sister, don't push your luck.

14:45.200 --> 14:46.280
Wait a second.

16:04.480 --> 16:06.400
I ran too fast just now.

16:08.000 --> 16:09.040
It's a sense of ritual.

16:09.040 --> 16:09.970
Sense of ritual.

16:12.080 --> 16:13.320
I couldn't find candles.

16:13.320 --> 16:14.980
I'll use a glow stick instead.

16:16.560 --> 16:17.800
Come on, make a wish.

16:21.280 --> 16:22.240
Mom and Dad.

16:22.440 --> 16:24.520
I'm at the amusement park for my birthday again.

16:24.520 --> 16:26.280
Mutou is with me this time.

16:26.560 --> 16:27.760
Do you see?

16:37.440 --> 16:39.440
Yuanbao, send me some messages.

16:39.520 --> 16:40.580
To give me courage.

16:40.600 --> 16:42.280
My mom signed me up for cram school.

16:42.280 --> 16:43.840
The teacher kept us late today.

16:43.840 --> 16:44.920
It's a bit dark on the road.

16:44.920 --> 16:46.720
And I'm a little scared walking home alone.

16:46.720 --> 16:48.120
Ruirui, don't be afraid.

16:48.120 --> 16:49.080
I'm with you.

16:49.400 --> 16:51.120
Be safe by yourself.

16:51.280 --> 16:53.720
Let me know immediately if anything happens.

16:53.720 --> 16:55.800
Okay, I'll let you know when I arrive.

16:55.960 --> 16:57.920
I feel much better talking to you.

16:58.240 --> 17:00.170
You really are my little sunshine.

17:24.040 --> 17:24.680
Don't be afraid.

17:24.680 --> 17:25.880
I'm right beside you.

17:25.920 --> 17:27.650
They won't dare to do anything.

18:03.560 --> 18:04.360
What's wrong?

18:05.600 --> 18:06.720
It's nothing.

18:06.840 --> 18:09.040
It's not safe for a girl to walk at night.

18:09.480 --> 18:11.540
Don't take the small alleys anymore.

18:13.600 --> 18:14.680
Gong Yu.

18:16.240 --> 18:16.840
Well.

18:17.200 --> 18:18.440
Let's go.

19:15.200 --> 19:17.000
How much were these green beans?

19:17.120 --> 19:18.880
Three-fifty a catty. What about yours?

19:18.880 --> 19:19.960
Mine were three.

19:20.200 --> 19:21.680
Yours were cheaper, Mrs. Xiong.

19:21.680 --> 19:22.440
They're pretty good.

19:22.440 --> 19:23.720
Yeah, very fresh.

19:23.880 --> 19:25.010
I also bought these.

19:25.040 --> 19:26.840
Mrs. Wang, Mrs. Xiong.

19:26.960 --> 19:29.280
Just got back from grocery shopping?

19:30.760 --> 19:31.560
Hey, Li.

19:31.760 --> 19:33.800
Your scarf is exactly like mine.

19:35.160 --> 19:36.520
It really is.

19:37.080 --> 19:38.200
My son heard

19:38.600 --> 19:40.680
that buying mom a red scarf this year

19:40.840 --> 19:42.800
will bring her health and longevity.

19:42.800 --> 19:43.640
Look.

19:43.800 --> 19:46.160
He even insisted I wear it.

19:46.880 --> 19:48.680
My daughter said the same thing.

19:48.760 --> 19:49.800
That shows

19:50.160 --> 19:51.960
your kids care about you.

19:52.080 --> 19:53.340
You should be content.

19:53.440 --> 19:56.040
Content? How could I not be?

19:56.320 --> 19:58.520
Well, you guys keep chatting.

19:58.720 --> 20:00.980
I have something to do, so I'll get going.

20:04.280 --> 20:05.840
What we just said,

20:06.120 --> 20:07.760
did she take it the wrong way?

20:09.600 --> 20:12.560
If Mrs. Xiong's son were still around,

20:12.720 --> 20:14.520
he would have bought her one too.

20:17.120 --> 20:18.000
It's a little pricier.

20:18.000 --> 20:19.000
Because the material is good,

20:19.000 --> 20:20.840
the original price was ninety-nine.

20:20.840 --> 20:22.040
Now it's fifty.

20:22.360 --> 20:23.240
What about this one?

20:23.240 --> 20:24.000
The thin one.

20:24.840 --> 20:25.970
Ma'am, listen to me.

20:26.240 --> 20:27.840
The original price of this thin one is fifty.

20:27.840 --> 20:28.770
Now it's thirty.

20:33.120 --> 20:33.720
Thirty is enough.

20:33.720 --> 20:34.800
Just thirty.

20:34.840 --> 20:35.520
Thirty for this.

20:35.520 --> 20:36.480
I can't do thirty.

20:36.480 --> 20:37.920
I'd be losing money at thirty.

20:37.920 --> 20:39.380
It's the wholesale price.

20:45.280 --> 20:46.200
Try it on.

20:46.200 --> 20:47.720
You guys try it on and see.

20:57.360 --> 20:58.400
Grandma.

21:00.120 --> 21:00.980
Are you hungry?

21:01.120 --> 21:02.200
I'll cook right away.

21:02.200 --> 21:03.440
We'll eat soon.

21:04.680 --> 21:05.800
Grandma.

21:28.000 --> 21:29.040
Didn't they say

21:29.560 --> 21:31.400
giving Mom a red scarf this year

21:31.960 --> 21:34.090
would bring her health and a long life?

21:36.080 --> 21:38.440
I dreamed of my dad yesterday.

21:40.680 --> 21:41.920
He asked me to give you

21:42.040 --> 21:44.640
a brand-new red scarf on his behalf.

21:56.000 --> 21:57.960
Offer one to your mom too.

21:58.400 --> 22:00.920
Your mom loved red the most.

22:02.520 --> 22:04.600
Grandma, come here.

22:10.600 --> 22:11.680
Look.

22:23.640 --> 22:24.480
Grandma, I'm

22:26.080 --> 22:27.680
a little late.

22:28.000 --> 22:29.600
I also bought you a red scarf.

22:29.640 --> 22:30.080
Okay.

22:30.120 --> 22:32.380
Put them both on. It's double the effect.

22:32.520 --> 22:33.840
I'll wear them both.

22:34.720 --> 22:36.000
Auntie Wenying,

22:36.920 --> 22:38.000
try it on.

22:41.280 --> 22:43.340
I thought I could give you a surprise.

22:43.720 --> 22:45.800
I'll wear them all.

22:47.400 --> 22:48.680
I'll put them all on.

22:49.320 --> 22:50.360
It looks beautiful, Grandma.

22:50.360 --> 22:52.960
Mom, I bought this one for you.

22:53.120 --> 22:54.240
Put it on.

22:54.520 --> 22:55.360
I have one too?

22:55.400 --> 22:56.560
Of course.

22:57.080 --> 22:58.080
Here, child.

22:58.560 --> 22:59.640
You wear it too.

23:00.040 --> 23:01.170
Thank you, Grandma.

23:01.720 --> 23:02.080
Here.

23:02.080 --> 23:03.040
Put one on Yuanbao too.

23:03.040 --> 23:04.500
Put one on our Yuanbao too.

23:05.320 --> 23:06.160
Thank you, Grandma.

23:06.160 --> 23:07.800
We're all happy.

23:08.280 --> 23:10.080
Right, to celebrate Yuanbao

23:10.160 --> 23:11.560
winning the essay contest,

23:11.560 --> 23:14.280
Auntie bought you pig trotters and ribs.

23:16.080 --> 23:17.240
Grandma.

23:18.800 --> 23:20.120
Mom.

23:20.360 --> 23:22.520
This brat, really.

23:35.680 --> 23:37.240
The kids have grown up.

23:38.480 --> 23:39.740
They are sensible now.

23:41.320 --> 23:43.520
Yuanbao won a prize in the essay contest.

23:43.520 --> 23:47.400
Tiejun and Aihua can finally rest in peace.

23:47.920 --> 23:48.760
Yes.

23:50.000 --> 23:51.000
For the kids,

23:51.320 --> 23:53.520
you've taken on so many part-time jobs.

23:54.640 --> 23:55.770
You've worked hard.

23:55.920 --> 23:56.880
Not at all.

23:58.280 --> 24:01.680
This way, we owe them a little less.

24:03.200 --> 24:03.920
Owe?

24:04.000 --> 24:05.080
Alright.

24:05.720 --> 24:06.960
Don't dwell on it.

24:13.200 --> 24:15.000
That very night,

24:15.200 --> 24:16.800
after I sent you the message,

24:16.880 --> 24:18.960
I was walking alone on the path home.

24:19.160 --> 24:20.760
The situation was tense.

24:20.960 --> 24:22.360
There were a few delinquents

24:22.360 --> 24:23.520
whistling at me.

24:23.600 --> 24:24.240
He

24:24.640 --> 24:26.840
suddenly appeared behind me.

24:27.160 --> 24:29.200
He escorted me through that

24:29.320 --> 24:31.960
most dangerous and darkest road.

24:32.760 --> 24:35.080
But the situation was so urgent at the time.

24:35.080 --> 24:36.160
I was terrified.

24:36.800 --> 24:39.080
I didn't even ask for his contact information.

24:39.080 --> 24:41.120
I only heard someone call him,

24:41.360 --> 24:42.240
Gong Yu.

24:42.920 --> 24:44.850
Don't you think it's frustrating?

24:45.960 --> 24:46.760
Right.

24:52.120 --> 24:54.600
Oh no. It got smudged by the rain.

24:55.080 --> 24:57.200
How am I supposed to return his umbrella?

24:57.200 --> 24:59.360
Who is it? Someone new?

24:59.600 --> 25:00.400
A guy or a girl?

25:00.480 --> 25:02.540
It was after that essay competition.

25:02.960 --> 25:04.280
It suddenly started raining.

25:04.280 --> 25:06.000
Then I almost got hit by a car.

25:06.320 --> 25:08.580
And suddenly a guy appeared and saved me.

25:09.040 --> 25:10.640
He even gave me his umbrella.

25:11.440 --> 25:13.120
I just want his contact info

25:13.200 --> 25:14.800
and return the umbrella to him.

25:14.800 --> 25:16.200
Oh my.

25:17.440 --> 25:19.840
This is more like an idol drama than my life.

25:20.040 --> 25:21.080
Is he handsome?

25:21.200 --> 25:23.920
A little bit. He looks like Aaron Kwok.

25:24.240 --> 25:25.400
Aaron Kwok?

25:31.080 --> 25:32.200
Oh my.

25:33.080 --> 25:35.160
You must be regretting it so much.

25:37.280 --> 25:38.640
It's fine.

25:38.920 --> 25:41.320
It's just that I can't return his umbrella.

25:41.760 --> 25:42.520
Will he think

25:42.520 --> 25:44.360
that I don't keep my word?

25:45.800 --> 25:48.400
Here, why don't you leave the umbrella with me?

25:48.600 --> 25:50.600
So you won't get upset looking at it.

25:56.880 --> 25:57.920
Oh my.

25:58.280 --> 26:00.320
This is your favorite Hu Ge sticker.

26:00.480 --> 26:02.520
Best friends share everything.

26:02.560 --> 26:03.760
Give me the notebook.

26:08.280 --> 26:10.160
Are you sure this is okay?

26:15.120 --> 26:16.800
It does look a bit weird.

26:18.480 --> 26:19.440
Forget it.

26:19.760 --> 26:20.960
Let's just go with it.

26:21.200 --> 26:23.000
When I want to see the whole face,

26:24.040 --> 26:26.100
I'll come to you to piece it together.

26:29.000 --> 26:31.800
When you met that guy,

26:32.160 --> 26:33.760
how did you feel?

26:38.160 --> 26:41.840
It's a feeling deep in your heart.

26:43.040 --> 26:46.480
It's like this person is braving the wind

26:46.640 --> 26:48.440
and coming just for you.

26:48.840 --> 26:51.200
You start to frequently

26:51.400 --> 26:54.320
and involuntarily think about it.

27:02.360 --> 27:03.360
You're done, bro.

27:04.120 --> 27:05.240
You've fallen.

27:10.120 --> 27:10.850
What is this?

27:11.080 --> 27:13.140
Self-Cultivation of Charming Boys.

27:18.080 --> 27:19.140
What are you doing?

27:21.440 --> 27:23.280
Why aren't ours growing?

27:24.800 --> 27:26.480
I don't know either.

27:27.000 --> 27:29.040
Maybe we should eat more papaya.

27:29.640 --> 27:30.480
By the way.

27:33.760 --> 27:34.720
This is

27:34.840 --> 27:37.000
the latest magazine my dad brought back

27:37.000 --> 27:38.800
from his business trip to Guangzhou.

27:38.800 --> 27:41.440
It's full of the most popular clothes,

27:41.720 --> 27:43.360
makeup, and hairstyles right now.

27:43.360 --> 27:44.840
This is good. This is good.

27:44.960 --> 27:46.080
This is good.

27:48.400 --> 27:49.920
Why does this look...

27:49.920 --> 27:51.980
It looks a bit like a delinquent girl.

27:53.400 --> 27:54.520
This is good. Long hair, short hair.

27:54.520 --> 27:55.720
This suits us.

27:55.920 --> 27:59.360
I didn't give all my New Year's money to my mom.

28:00.600 --> 28:02.000
Let's go. Hurry up.

28:31.720 --> 28:33.040
What's with this look?

28:34.160 --> 28:35.160
Does it look good?

28:35.640 --> 28:37.720
Ruirui forced me to do it.

28:38.760 --> 28:39.640
I still think

28:39.680 --> 28:41.410
your previous look was better.

28:44.800 --> 28:46.130
Then I'll go wash it off.

28:47.080 --> 28:48.520
Luckily it's temporary.

28:49.520 --> 28:51.320
Saying I'd turn into a princess.

28:51.440 --> 28:52.480
It's all a lie.

28:52.880 --> 28:54.740
You care so much about my opinion.

28:54.760 --> 28:57.240
Are you trying to get my attention?

29:00.400 --> 29:01.560
Is it okay now?

29:29.520 --> 29:30.640
I'm talking to you.

29:34.160 --> 29:35.690
Isn't it the same as before?

29:40.800 --> 29:42.260
What's wrong with my face?

29:44.520 --> 29:46.440
Forget it. It's hopeless.

29:47.000 --> 29:48.280
Crazy.

30:13.840 --> 30:15.080
The floor is slippery.

30:15.080 --> 30:17.010
Be careful when you walk next time.

30:18.040 --> 30:19.400
I'm leaving first.

30:26.480 --> 30:27.720
Mu Qingjun.

30:40.000 --> 30:40.640
Stand up.

30:41.720 --> 30:44.680
Hello, teacher.

30:44.880 --> 30:46.810
Hello, students. Please sit down.

30:49.560 --> 30:50.280
Today,

30:50.720 --> 30:52.120
we have a new student transferring to our class.

30:52.120 --> 30:54.520
Let's welcome him with a round of applause.

31:10.200 --> 31:12.160
Mr. Tian, is there anything wrong?

31:12.800 --> 31:14.200
I'm fine. Are you?

31:19.360 --> 31:20.600
You went to the wrong class.

31:20.600 --> 31:21.480
Sorry.

31:23.520 --> 31:25.120
What are you all laughing at?

31:25.320 --> 31:26.560
You two, come in.

31:42.960 --> 31:44.720
This is so unreal.

31:44.880 --> 31:46.800
He actually transferred to our class.

31:46.800 --> 31:49.040
Is God finally awake?
